description: Order of simple Chevalley group B_6(q), q = prime power.
references: H. S. M. Coxeter and W. O. J. Moser, Generators and Relations for Discrete Groups, 4th ed., Springer-Verlag, NY, reprinted 1984, p. 131.
J. H. Conway, R. T. Curtis, S. P. Norton, R. A. Parker and R. A. Wilson, ATLAS of Finite Groups. Oxford Univ. Press, 1985, p. xvi.
formula: a(n) = b(A000961(n + 1), 6) where b(q,n) is defined in A003927. - _Sean A. Irvine_, Sep 22 2015
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
